title: 103 The Power of Clarity – 5 Steps to Achieving Any Goal
description:
"You've got to figure out what you want first or you'll be given whatever others didn't want that was left over." - Lewis Howes
If you enjoyed the show and would like to know more, head over to www.lewishowes.com/103 for show notes and more.
